node.text:
My @roger_dubuis ‘Secret List’ challenge 1 out of 12 has been approved!!!
🍾💯
If you haven’t watched my recent YouTube vlog yet, please throw IG away for 10 min and go check it out. Then you’ll totally understand what I’m talking about!

This challenge was “Take Your Timepiece To The Sky” and I thought that literally flying from the French Riviera to Lombok with a paraglide was probably the nicest way to do it… took a while, but was definitely worth it!

Now it’s time to enjoy some proper nice tropical time! 🌴🌊

Huge thanks to @roquebruneparapente & @dodi.lombok for these incredible flights 🦅

Music @toutant 🖤

#RogerDubuis #NoRulesOurGame

node.text:
Not everyday you can film and also drive such an incredible car!
NEW VLOG IS LIVE 💣 link in Bio

This is the intro of my vlog! I really put such a wild energy on the filming and editing of this piece. It’s pretty hard to translate how a car feels, and I truly hope it does it to you now! If not, open your computer, head to my YouTube and watch it in 4K with the loudest speakers you have!
Then let me know what you and your neighbors think hahaha 😘 

What a time we had with @florianmerckx pushing this car how it’s supposed to be pushed, and @jonolsson1 and I trying to stay alive on the passenger seat!

Huge thx again to @scuderiamontecarlo & @balco the proper session! 🤘🏻❤️

node.text:
New vlog is up you know wherewith a serious challenge:

Is it possible to surf, skate and snowboard, all in 1 day? 🏄🏼‍♂️🛹🏂 

Since I was a kid I had this challenge stuck in my head. But having the right conditions to do all 3 here in the French Riviera is almost impossible. But I personally like challenges and I like to spice them even more!
I asked my friends @antoinetruchet & @florianmerckx if they wanted to join the challenge and also asked @mercedeseq if I could borrow the brand new 100%⚡️EQA I tested couple weeks before and see if I could do this whole trip on 1 single charge! 

Honestly we had a pure blast the whole day and I hope the full video will translate it as much as it possibly can ❤️
Any feedback on the video? Lemme know in the comments and let’s chat 🤓

Music: @jnathyn - Dioma

node.text:
The mustang vlog is live on my YouTube! Link in my bio 🐎
Anyone already watched it? 🍿
This vlog really represents something special to me. I’ve been dreaming about this exact day for a really long time. I actually never thought I would be able to make it happen one day. This is a good reminder to each and every single one of you. Remember to dream big and to always push yourself in the right direction in order to make it happen one day!
The biggest thank to my friend @nicolas_gaillard for the incredible fpv shots! 🤘🏻

100k views on my latest YouTube video! 💯🔥

To thank you guys I decided to do a little compilation of all the best clips @nicolas_gaillard and I filmed while putting this one-off electric beast to the test @mercedesbenz ! 👊🏻

Hope you like it and if you haven’t watched the full video yet, you know where to find it 😘

Music: Clarx - Shakedown [NCS Release]

node.text:
So happy to finally announce I’m now officially part of the @roger_dubuis tribe! 🤘🏻
@jonolsson1 and I have been working with @roger_dubuis for years now on so many incredible projects!
And I’m really looking forward for all the upcoming ones! 🔥 
I mean who know a watch maker who would let you Ollie in their shop and bomb downhill on a skateboard while wearing this incredible timepiece, the Excalibur Spider Huracán Performante!

Thanks for the filming help @florianmerckx 😎

node.text:
Finally reunited with @jonolsson1 for couple weeks of pure holidays! 🔥 And one of the first activities was of course to go ride the @fliteboard at sunset from @rickarddeler brand new Helena yacht!! 💪
We were already having a blast, and then a group of dolphins just decided to join the party and play with us! 🐬 
Honestly the most unreal experience I’ve ever got the chance to live! I really hope the video does translate how crazy it felt 😅✔️
Who watched the vlog yet?? 🤔Don’t forget to watch it on the biggest screen you have, preferably on a cinema haha and with the volume all the way to the top! 🤯❤️

Music: 
Besomorph & Arcando & Neoni - Army [NCS Release]

node.text:
New vlog is out on my YouTube! Did you guys already watch it?🔥
Link in my bio!

Of course you know me, a road trip with a @lamborghini = a Light Painting session! 👊

Such a mission to get to that perfect spot up in Arvidsjaur, Sweden! 🙌

It was midnight and we drove for hours before finding this perfect location with deep powder, surrounded by trees, with no lights around and especially no other cars or people! 😄

Music @snavs 
Thank u for the help that night @chri_koch @atropatesis and the 2 military guys who helped us found the spot!
.
.
#lamborghini #urus #ssuv #supercar #LightPainting #lamborghiniurus #lighttrails #aftereffects

node.text:
New Vlog live on YouTube!

I never had the chance to finish this vlog until now and I felt that you might like some winter vibes now that summer has started!
@teamgalag SnowTour Vol.3 ❄️ is back!

Much love to @lamborghini for the beauty ❤️ and to @olle_olsson and his @sqncsweden team for setting up the mind blowing heli chase! I still can’t believe we did this!
Honestly the most amount of chills and adrenaline shocks I’ve had in a long time!

Song: @snavs - 2018 - Intro

node.text:
Happy 2022 you all ❤️
Please, spray snow, not champagne 🥂 
Hope everyone had a beautiful end of 2021, and kick off 2022 in the best possible way!

Don’t forget that a new year is a good way to create some good habits and become a better person. So go ahead, let’s agree to do better this year and to become the best version of yourself 🤘🏻
Much love to you all 😘

Follow cam by el master @abekislevitz over this beauty NYE weekend in @mammothmountain 🍾🍾🍾

node.text:
I have never really been a huge fan of selfies, but that day was definitely an exception.
Casually sharing a little pose next to a 8m whale shark with a 1,5m wide smile!
🐋🙂

This is just our little reminder for you to never be normal 😘
And not to dance on the edge of a boat, except if you are well trained, and you pretend you know what you are doing! 🤸‍♂️

Thank you for all the support you show us for todays new FW21 @cestnormal drop! I’m personally so looking forward to see you all impeccably be matching wearing our new red color at your xmas family diners! Please send us all the photos we want to see them all!
 Much love to you all again ❤️

node.text:
30 f*cking years old 🥂

Few days ago I had the chance to celebrate my 30th bd surrounded with my favorite ones ❤️ here are a few raw and less raw clips of what went down on my bd and also throughout this beautiful @cestnormal week in Cyprus!

1_ la famille ❤️
2_by far the best wake up call of my past 30years
3_finaaaaaally reunited with my parents @jonolsson1 & @jannid and meeting my sister Leia for the first time
4_still haven’t figure out if this bd dinner was a dream or actual reality? 🤔😍
5_we ate Colette for desert 🎂 
6_cyprus showing us how cool it is to be in Cyprus 🐢
7_try to spot the high five
8_getting ready for some actual work…
9_because we needed to shoot the upcoming @cestnormal collection 😅

So much love for this incredible time and everyone that made this week so special!
❤️

node.text:
Sunsets in Lombok just keep on exceeding my expectations every single time. I have been here for almost 6 months now and it feels like everyday is just getting better.

Today i just looked at some of the 1000’s of photos I shot while shooting the GoPro Hero 10 campaign and I found so many beautiful one that I guess I never had the time to work on and share before! 

Please welcome the first one of them, will share more later on. I hope you will enjoy them as much as I do. if you do, and also if you made it that far, you can leave a 😘 under this photo, that way I will know that you are a real human haha

Bisous

@gopro #GoProHERO10 #H102021

node.text:
There are some feelings in life that are impossible to express, especially just through one single image.
But this, let me tell you, was an extraordinary experience, one of the most memorable in my life and barely no words will ever be able to describe it!

Fortunately I filmed it all and made one of my favorite video so far (the most recent @gopro video that I posted on my YouTube 2 days ago). I hope it will help to translate how crazy of an experience it was!

If you feel like getting a better glimpse at this adventure, you know where to find my video 😘

Thanks again @gopro for believing in my work and letting me be apart of this very special #HERO10 launch 🤘🏻❤️
 
📸 @ivarmathias shot on GoPro #hero10black

node.text:
My Rinjani cleanup ‘vlog’ is finally online on YouTube! (Link in my bio!!) Come watch the whole story on how we manage to remove 1.6 tons of trash in 72h from Rinjani Volcano 🌋 

Please share this Reels in your story so we can reach and educate as many people as possible about this issue… ❤️

This is by far the video I spent the most amount time on, almost 3 weeks! This cleanup mission we undertook with @greenrinjani_ was definitely not an easy one to document and no need to tell you how hard it was to sort the hundreds (or maybe even thousands) of clips I had recorded haha…

My initial timeline was over 5h of usable footage, that I reduced into an 1h30 film which I then managed to squeeze down to 40min 🥵
On top of that in order to amplify the emotion throughout the video, I decided to download all the stems of each music separately so I could really play with them the way I wanted! 

So yeah if you haven’t watched it yet, I do believe it worth taking those 40min off your next Netflix show and watch this instead 😘
(And don’t hesitate to watch it on a big screen and with a proper sound system 🤘🏻)

Photo animation by @creyety 📸 
.
.
.
.
.
